{"title":"Flex布局深度指南","slug":"CSS/Flex布局深度指南","date":"2023-07-12T12:33:36.000Z","updated":"2025-08-08T16:57:50.747Z","comments":false,"path":"api/articles/CSS/Flex布局深度指南.json","photos":[],"excerpt":"现代化布局解决方案精要","covers":null,"content":"<p><strong>核心属性组合拳</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"CSS\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.container</span> &#123;<br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: flex;<br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex-flow</span>: row wrap; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 方向+换行 */</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">justify-content</span>: space-evenly; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 主轴对齐 */</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">align-content</span>: stretch; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 多行对齐 */</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.item</span> &#123;<br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">200px</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 增长 收缩 基础 */</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">align-self</span>: center; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 单个项目对齐 */</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n\n<p>常见问题解决方案：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>等高分栏：align-items: stretch (默认值)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>底部对齐：margin-top: auto</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>流式网格：flex-basis: calc(33% - 20px)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>垂直居中：justify-content: center; align-items: center</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":2,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS3","slug":"CSS3","count":1,"path":"api/tags/CSS3.json"},{"name":"Flexbox","slug":"Flexbox","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Flexbox.json"}]}